articles.title: EXCLUSIVE: BCCI Debunks Pakistan Media's Claim On Hybrid Model Asia Cup, Provides Update On WC Venues - Times Now
articles.description: Speaking exclusively to Timesnownews.com, a BCCI official has denied claims that BCCI has agreed to Pakistan Cricket Board's (PCB) hybrid model to host the Asia Cup 2023. The ODI World Cup 2023 is expected to begin on October 5, and the decision on venues is …
